data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: This picture shows information about an athlete in a competition. From the image, we can see that a male athlete in white sports clothing is kneeling on the ground. From the picture, we can see that the audiences behind him are watching and applauding him. According to the image, we can find that a paramedic wearing orange pants is trying to help him stand up. I think this athlete must feel very tired and exhausted after the competition. (78字)
